selecttranslate (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release of SelectTranslate
  * Instant translation of selected text using Apertium engine
  * Automatic text selection monitoring
  * Simple GTK3 interface with dynamic layouts
  * Dictionary lookup functionality
  * Smart cursor-relative window positioning
  * Clean and intuitive user experience
  * System package dependencies instead of pip packages

 -- Jorge Sanabria <js@jorels.com>  Wed, 09 Jul 2025 12:00:00 +0000